    </div>
    <span xlink:href="10640_2018_231_Article_IEq45.gif" class="inline-graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
   </div>
  </div> is the elasticity of intertemporal substitution. Both relative risk aversion and relative intergenerational inequality aversion are equal 1/
  <span class="italic">σ</span>. Equation (
